Hello World for creating a ShinyApp that pulls data from SQLServer 

1. Install the latest version of RStudio Desktop from https://www.rstudio.com/
2. Download the HelloWorld App from https://github.com/mhahsler/ShinyApp_DB_HelloWorld
3. Follow the instructions to create the database and record the credentials.
4. Follow the instructions in app.R

Contact your instructor with questions.

Good Luck!